Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<ColumnDescriptor>, org.apache.thrift.TBase<ColumnDescriptor._Fields>
public class ColumnDescriptor
extends Object
implements org.apache.thrift.TBase<ColumnDescriptor._Fields>, Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<ColumnDescriptor>

An HColumnDescriptor contains information about a column family such as the number of versions, compression settings, etc. It is used as input when creating a table or adding a column.
